Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.64,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Always　 醒めきってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.81,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}速すぎる  Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:26.93,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明な闇に囲まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:30.42,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も似た網の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:33.63,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Found you  あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.87,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れ動いたPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:38.30,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:43.29,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全てキミに会うためのProcessだったね
