Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------OPCHNlrc----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.89,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去往不斷延展的天邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:02.34,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明的翅膀將我引領
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:05.87,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}它在遠方靜待著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:11.26,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛往未曾預見的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.64,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理智清醒時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.81,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時常感到日夜流逝過快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:26.93,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}四周被透明的黑暗包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:30.42,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們都活在寸步難移的網中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:33.63,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尋覓你  每當風吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.87,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中激情彷彿隨風躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:38.30,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:43.29,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切皆為與你相會的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.24,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.86,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:52.74,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遠方傳來的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.67,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我不禁加快心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.52,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.02,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:07.36,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光輝灑下  我逐漸甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:11.08,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要你我互信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.33,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.50,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.98,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼前景色將煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:20.45,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昔日傷痕亦成今日榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:25.10,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因此與你一起超越重力的束縛
